{"id":1081,"date":"2022-12-11T17:47:23","modified":"2025-09-16T07:15:41","slug":"star-atlas-guide","link":"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/","title":{"rendered":"How to play Star Atlas guide"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Intergalactic Herald has created a guide on how to play <a href=\"https:\/\/staratlas.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas<\/a>. This &#8220;how to play Star Atlas guide&#8221; is a step-by-step outline of everything you need to get started with Star Atlas. The guide has three main parts:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Star Atlas Beginner Guide &#8211; This part explains cryptocurrency, Marketplace, Faction Fleet and getting into the Showroom.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Play Star Atlas with $100 and $20 per month &#8211; This part demonstrates one possible way to play Star Atlas for a typical gamer with a modest budget.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How to play Star Atlas SAGE Labs (Starbased) Beginner Guide &#8211; This part shows how to play one of the parts of Star Atlas called SAGE Labs (Starbased) which is playable in a web browser.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The guide also includes links to other Star Atlas content creators, resources and tools. Check out the table of content below if you want to jump around.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em><mark style=\"background-color:#fcb900;color:#000000\" class=\"has-inline-color\">NOTE:  Many of the videos show a previous version of the Star Atlas game user interface.  Star Atlas is constantly being developed but the game play concepts in the videos are still relevant.<\/mark><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#fcb900\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> <\/mark> <\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Each individual article is below but if you are ready to get started in a step-by-step guide workflow, click the button and start with the first step on each part of the Star Atlas Beginner Guide.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-vertical is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-a1ed0a01 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-buy-cryptocurrency\/\">Start Beginner Guide &#8211; Buy cryptocurrency<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-overview\/\">Start Play Start Atlas Guide &#8211; Overview<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-play-star-atlas-sage-labs-starbased-overview\/\">Start Play SAGE Labs (Starbased) Guide &#8211; Overview<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Table of Contents<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#cryptocurrency\">Cryptocurrency<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#marketplace\">Marketplace<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#score\">Faction Fleet\/SCORE<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#preseason\">Preseason<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#showroom\">Showroom<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#holosim\">Holosim<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#play\">Play Star Atlas with $100 and $20 per month<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#sage\">SAGE<\/a> &#8211; Star Atlas: Golden Era<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#starbased\">SAGE Labs (Starbased)<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#sage-tools\">SAGE Tools<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#crew\">Crew<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#fleet-viewer\">Fleet Viewer<\/a> &#8211; retired<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"#sagelabs\">SAGE Labs<\/a> &#8211; retired<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Here is some general Star Atlas information:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/what-is-star-atlas\/\">What is Star Atlas<\/a>? &#8211; Watch the Star Atlas trailer video.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Join the Star Atlas Discord? &#8211; Join the <a href=\"https:\/\/discord.com\/invite\/staratlas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas Discord<\/a> server to become part of the community.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/portal.productboard.com\/staratlas\/1-star-atlas-roadmap\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas Roadmap<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/podcast\/podcast-50-star-atlas-interview-beginner-guide-to-lore-of-star-atlas\/\">Beginner Guide to Lore of Star Atlas<\/a> &#8211; interview with Jos\u00e9 Siqueira from Star Atas. Jos\u00e9 is the Lore Smith of Star Atlas.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/j55vrZNwqEQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas Gameplay Walkthrough with CEO Michael Wagner<\/a> &#8211; Walkthrough of Star Atlas Showroom and SAGE.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"cryptocurrency\">Cryptocurrency<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Star Atlas is a game based on web3 technology like cryptocurrency.  Assets in the game are NFTs (non-fungible token) like ships.  Star Atlas has an economy and governance that uses <a href=\"https:\/\/support.staratlas.com\/knowledge\/star-atlas-tokens\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">crypto coins<\/a> of ATLAS and POLIS.  So, to get involved in the game, you need to purchase cryptocurrency on the Solana blockchain.  Below are the steps to get started in cryptocurrency.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-buy-cryptocurrency\/\">How to buy cryptocurrency<\/a>? &#8211; Create account on Coinbase<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-buy-sol-on-coinbase\/\">How to buy SOL on Coinbase<\/a>? &#8211; Purchase cryptocurrency in the form of SOL (Solana coin)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-create-phantom-wallet\/\">How to create a Phantom wallet<\/a>? &#8211; Create a software cryptocurrency wallet to interact with Star Atlas<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-send-cryptocurrency-from-coinbase-to-phantom-wallet\/\">How to send cryptocurrency from Coinbase to wallet<\/a>? &#8211; Learn to send SOL to your crypto wallet<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-swap-between-sol-and-usdc\/\">How to swap between between SOL and USDC<\/a>? &#8211; Learn to swap between different cryptocurrency<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-buy-star-atlas-atlas\/\">How to buy Star Atlas ATLAS<\/a>? &#8211; Purchase ATLAS coin which is used in Star Atlas as an utility token<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-buy-star-atlas-polis\/\">How to buy Star Atlas POLIS<\/a>? &#8211; Purchase POLIS coin which is used in Star Atlas for governance <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-setup-a-ledger-using-phantom-wallet\/\">How to setup Ledger using Phantom for Star Atlas<\/a>? (optional) &#8211; Learn how to setup a hardware wallet to be used through a software wallet<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">ATLAS and POLIS Buying Guide by Beyond the Horizon<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/BTH2620\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Beyond the Horizon 2620<\/a> has created a couple of videos on how to purchase the Star Atlas coins: ATLAS and POLIS<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=2oQNy5k-PO8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How To Buy ATLAS<\/a>: The Star Atlas In-Game Currency<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=L0mjF0jHMiY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How To Buy POLIS<\/a>: The Star Atlas Governance Token<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"marketplace\">Star Atlas Marketplace<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The Star Atlas Marketplace is a place to purchase Star Atlas items.  But, you can also sell them to other buyers.  The main item to buy and sell are Star Atlas ships.  But you can find other Star Atlas items like posters, badges and land.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-connect-wallet-to-star-atlas\/\">How to connect your wallet to the Star Atlas website<\/a>? &#8211; Connect your Phantom wallet to the Star Atlas website to authorize Star Atlas transactions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-pick-a-faction-in-star-atlas\/\">How to pick a faction in Star Atlas<\/a>? &#8211; Pick from one of the three Star Atlas factions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-buy-star-atlas-ship\/\">How to buy a Star Atlas ship<\/a>? &#8211; Purchase a Star Atlas ship in the MarketPlace<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-sell-a-star-atlas-ship\/\">How to sell a Star Atlas ship<\/a>? (optional) &#8211; Sell a Star Atlas ship in the MarketPlace <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"score\">Faction Fleet\/SCORE<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The Faction Fleet or SCORE (Ship Commissions on Remote Expeditions) is an aspect of Star Atlas where you can enroll your Star Atlas ships.  By keeping your ships supplied with the necessary resources, you will earn rewards in the form of the ATLAS token.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-enlist-your-star-atlas-ship-in-faction-fleet-score\/\">How to enlist your Star Atlas ship in Faction Fleet\/SCORE<\/a>? &#8211; Enlist your Star Atlas ships to earn rewards of ATLAS<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-buy-resources-star-atlas-marketplace\/\">How to buy resources in the Star Atlas Marketplace<\/a>? Buy resources to supply your Star Atlas ship<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-resupply-your-star-atlas-ship-in-faction-fleet-score\/\">How to resupply your ships in Faction Fleet\/SCORE<\/a>? Add resources to your Star Atlas ship<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-claim-star-atlas-rewards-in-faction-fleet-score\/\">How to claim Star Atlas ship rewards in Faction Fleet\/SCORE<\/a>? Claim ATLAS rewards<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-remove-ship-from-faction-fleet-score\/\">How to remove ship from Faction Fleet\/SCORE<\/a>? (optional) Remove Star Atlas ship<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"preseason\">Preseason<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Preseason is the name of a version of the Star Atlas game being developed using the Unreal Engine. The game is currently being developed but many aspects are available to experience now in a &#8220;private&#8221; pre-alpha state.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The game is available to download and install on a Windows computer from the Epic Games Store. Information on the installation process can be found right below under the <a href=\"#showroom\">Showroom<\/a> section but the method to get a game code has been made easier. A <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-game-code\/\">game code<\/a> can be obtained in the Star Atlas Discord.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The Preseason version has a number of gameplay experiences.  The list below will show screenshots of the different experiences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-initial-loading-screens\/\">Initial Loading Screens<\/a> &#8211; initial game screens after starting game<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-fleet-command\/\">Fleet Command <\/a>&#8211; a new way to experience the Star Atlas economy similar to SAGE<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-hosting\/\">Hosting<\/a> &#8211; Hosting and joining game sessions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Training &#8211; There are a number of different ways to gain experience by training in Star Atlas\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-training-spaceship-dogfight\/\">Spaceship Dogfight<\/a> &#8211; pilot a spaceship in space and dogfight other spaceships<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-training-gunplay\/\">Gunplay<\/a> &#8211; practice gunplay mode with bots<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-training-volant-station\/\">Volant Station<\/a> &#8211; load your spaceship into the showroom<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-training-racing-tracks\/\">Racing Tracks<\/a> &#8211; experience two different racing tracks<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-training-oni-css\/\">ONI CSS<\/a> &#8211; ONI faction Central Space Station with many districts and housing structures.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-galia\/\">Galia<\/a> &#8211; explore space and planets in a seemless transition. Hold the &#8220;B&#8221; key to enable subwarp.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The Star Atlas game can be controlled using <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/preseason-keyboard-commands\/\">keyboard commands<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https:\/\/x.com\/KILLxTHISxGUY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">KILLxxTHISxxGUY<\/a> created a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=4D6Rm-B87z0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">shooter beginner video guide<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"showroom\">Showroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em><mark style=\"background-color:#fcb900;color:#000000\" class=\"has-inline-color\">NOTE:  Many of the videos show a previous version of the Star Atlas game user interface.  Star Atlas is constantly being developed but the game play concepts in the videos are still relevant.<\/mark><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#fcb900\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> <\/mark> <\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The Showroom is the first chance to interact in the Star Atlas metaverse using the Unreal Engine 5 environment.  The Showroom is software to install on your Windows computer to then enter a 3D world where you can create a character and interact with your Star Atlas ships and explore an expanding environment. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>How to <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-install-star-atlas-showroom\/\">install Star Atlas Showroom<\/a>?<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How to <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-get-game-code-for-star-atlas-showroom\/\">get game code for Star Atlas Showroom<\/a>?<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How to <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-login-to-star-atlas-showroom\/\">login to Star Atlas Showroom<\/a>?<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How to use <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-use-ledger-with-star-atlas-showroom\/\">Ledger with the Star Atlas Showroom<\/a>? (optional)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Additional guides<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Tips and tricks for <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/tips-tricks-racing-star-atlas-showroom\/\">racing in Star Atlas Showroom<\/a> by MetaVerse Explorer<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=GIVol7AkCO8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Photography tutorial<\/a> by Falkor<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"holosim\"><strong>Holosim<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Star Atlas has released a new game in &#8220;beta&#8221; called Holosim.  Holosim is a free to play simulation of SAGE, the browser-based game.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Beyond the Horizon created a video walkthrough series.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=ZF4B4-C9_10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas Holosim Tutorial Walkthrough (Part 1)<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=C7CECQ_m65I\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: Holosim Tutorial Walkthrough (Part 2)<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"play\"><strong>Play Star Atlas with $100 and $20 per month<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This guide goes through all the steps to buy tokens, ships, claim stake and resources.  Then it shows other ways to interact with the Star Atlas game.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-overview\/\">Overview<\/a> &#8211; overview, prerequisites and caveats of playing Star Atlas with $100 and $20 per month<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-tokens\/\">Tokens<\/a> &#8211; how to swap for different Star Atlas tokens like ATLAS and POLIS<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-buy-ships-claim-stake\/\">Buy ships and claim stake<\/a> &#8211; buy two Star Atlas ships and one claim stake<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-claim-stake\/\">Stake claim stake<\/a> &#8211; stake a Star Atlas claim stake to claim rewards of food, fuel, ammo and toolkits<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-buy-resources\/\">Buy resources<\/a> &#8211; how to purchase Star Atlas resources of food, fuel, ammo and toolkits<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-faction-fleet\/\">Enlist in Faction Fleet<\/a> &#8211; enlist a Star Atlas ship in the Faction Fleet to claim rewards of ATLAS<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-20-per-month\/\">$20 per month<\/a> &#8211; why to pay $20 a month to continue playing Star Atlas<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-dao\/\">DAO<\/a> (Decentralized Autonomous Organization) &#8211; how to interact with the Star Atlas DAO using POLIS<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-showroom\/\">Showroom<\/a> &#8211; how to start playing the 3D Unreal Engine game in the Star Atlas Showroom<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-sage-labs-starbased\/\">SAGE Labs (Starbased)<\/a> &#8211; how to start playing the web browser game in SAGE Labs (Starbased)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/play-star-atlas-with-100-and-20-per-month-marketplace\/\">Marketplace<\/a> &#8211; how to start playing with buying and selling in the Star Atlas Marketplace<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"sage\">SAGE &#8211; Star Atlas: Golden Era<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em><mark style=\"background-color:#fcb900;color:#000000\" class=\"has-inline-color\">NOTE:  Many of the videos show a previous version of the Star Atlas game user interface.  Star Atlas is constantly being developed but the game play concepts in the videos are still relevant.<\/mark><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#fcb900\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> <\/mark> <\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">SAGE is an in-browser game module of Star Atlas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/sage-game-manual-december-2022-draft\/\">SAGE Game Manual<\/a> &#8211; December 2022 Draft<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">SAGE vs SCORE<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/BTH2620\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Beyond the Horizon<\/a> has created a <a href=\"https:\/\/youtube.com\/playlist?list=PLSWtv8cdyR1mo_Mey8rH_OiFUbFG4MWEg&amp;si=-MfmqRl-BOq0Ge39\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">video series comparing SAGE and SCORE<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">SAGE Labs (Starbased)<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Guides from Aephia\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Starbased \u2013 The Missing Manual \u2013 <a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/starbased-the-missing-manual-part-0\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Part 0<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Starbased \u2013 The Missing Manual \u2013 <a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/starbased-the-missing-manual-part-1\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Part 1<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Starbased \u2013 The Missing Manual \u2013 <a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/starbased-the-missing-manual-part-2\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Part 2<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=DJTNQ5x-loI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How to play Starbased as a small player<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=ST2k1CYglsI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas SAGE Beginner Guide &amp; Tips For New Players<\/a> video tutorial from MetaVerse Explorer<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"starbased\">SAGE Labs (Starbased)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">SAGE Labs (Starbased) in a version of Star Atlas that is playable in a web browser.  You can move around your ships to mine and scan for resources.  Then you can move the cargo and craft other components.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-play-star-atlas-sage-labs-starbased-overview\/\">Overview<\/a> &#8211; overview, caveats and prerequisites<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-play-star-atlas-sage-labs-starbased-starting-game\/\">Starting game<\/a> &#8211; how to start SAGE Labs (Starbased) by creating a profile<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-play-star-atlas-sage-labs-starbased-adding-resources\/\">Adding resources<\/a> &#8211; add ships, create a fleet and add resources to the fleet<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-play-star-atlas-sage-labs-starbased-movement\/\">Movement<\/a> &#8211; how to move around Starbased using warp and subwarp<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-play-star-atlas-sage-labs-starbased-scanning\/\">Scanning<\/a> &#8211; how to scan for survey data units (SDUs)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-play-star-atlas-sage-labs-starbased-mining\/\">Mining<\/a> &#8211; how to mine for raw materials<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-play-star-atlas-sage-labs-starbased-cargo\/\">Cargo<\/a> &#8211; how to add and remove cargo along with transfer to a wallet<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/BTH2620\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Beyond the Horizon<\/a> created a two-part Starbased video tutorial. The two videos are a great way to see all the parts in action along with more in-depth on some of the Starbased topics like crew integration, crew crafting and Loyalty Point redemption.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=SnfuA1WdxHc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: SAGE Starbased Tutorial Part One<\/a> (2024)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=SA-hyIr0pfA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: SAGE Starbased Tutorial Part Two<\/a> (2024)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Beyond the Horizon created a video showing the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=pq3ZIQ0mGd4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">new user interface<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Local Markets<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Local Markets are a new feature in SAGE Labs (Starbased) which allow for a marketplace at each starbase.  Resources and materials can be brought and sold at the starbase.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Beyond the Horizon created a video on <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=HeV577mfFpU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Local Market gameplay<\/a>.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Aephia created a <a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/sage-local-markets\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Local Markets guide<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fleet Rentals<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Fleet Rentals are a new feature in SAGE Labs (Starbased) which allow gamers to create a fleet and then rent it out to other gamers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Beyond the Horizon created some videos about fleet rentals:\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=eDg7PlLAgoc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: Fleet Rentals Are Landing!!!<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=zJ9oeE2op7A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: Tips For Renting Out Your Fleets!<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=-WC9ilgUiFE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: Zero-2-Hero w\/ Fleet Rentals (PART 1)<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=iXd-Muyldjc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: Zero-2-Hero w\/ Fleet Rentals (PART 2)<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=d-BGOvvP094\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: Zero-2-Hero w\/ Fleet Rentals (PART 3)<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=I_BpKQwAOZM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: Zero-2-Hero w\/ Fleet Rentals (PART 4)<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=60X05j9acwM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas: Zero-2-Hero w\/ Fleet Rentals (PART 5)<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>DominicVain created a couple of videos about fleet rentals:\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Star Atlas Fleet Rentals &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=iNCW85zemTY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How to Borrow Ships from Other Players<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Star Atlas Fleet Rentals &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=QmpM_Go-n1U\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How to Loan Out Your Space Ships<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"sage-tools\">SAGE Tools<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/ImGroovin\/Lab-Assistant\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Lab Assistant by Shadow Local [SLY]<\/a> &#8211; This is a SAGE Labs tool to help track status and automate actions.  If you find the SLY Assistant helpful, please considering making a donation.  Their Solana address is at the bottom of their <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/ImGroovin\/SLY-Assistant\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">GitHub page<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/ImGroovin\/SLY-Assistant\/blob\/main\/README.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Readme<\/a> file for script<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Videos explaining the tool was created by <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/BTH2620\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Beyond the Horizon<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/SatoshiMama2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SatoshiMama<\/a>.  <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/9FTvp0DSbUk?si=5ps5IOFecNXLAjs7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Part 1<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/LZqwUjC1SEo?si=fIZbhMk1tBBb29u_\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">part 2<\/a>.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/mikatachan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">mikatachan<\/a> has created a <a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/document\/d\/1FQZl7UOXdj64vgc5rCVicPtDG7R2gl-lHEX3_bnWvKU\/edit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">great guide<\/a> to configuring SLY Assistant along with tips.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=c8SiBoeVsko\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SAGE Starbase Automation Tutorial<\/a> (from Aephia)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https:\/\/atlas.eveeye.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">EVEEYE<\/a> &#8211; EVEEYE is a tool to access more information in SAGE. Beyond the Horizon created an <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/4V-PuXqsxss?si=qP-6N2wIikNq73ti\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">overview video<\/a> and a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=MZmee7eZqUE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">second video<\/a> after some updates for SAGE Starbased.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"crew\">Crew<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Crew are another aspect of Star Atlas.  Crew can be in ships or perform crafting tasks<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Beyond the Horizon has created an <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/xYJad--g8aI?si=HFpq1EpQiR7t54mT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">introduction to Crew Packs<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trading crew on Tensor<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Beyond the Horizon &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/4LCJqJfIykM?si=P0hoWvspZFM7_YHr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tensor Tutorial<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Crafting<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>MetaVerse Explorer &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=zjEr-mC-pFM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas Guide &#8211; Making Money with Crafters<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Real Estate<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Star Atlas has real estate you can purchase within the game.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https:\/\/galiameta.io\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Galia Meta<\/a> published an article about <a href=\"https:\/\/galiameta.io\/galia-real-estate\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Galia Real Estate<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=l_fEVg1v4xA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ONI CSS Tour, by The Empress<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=cLkHNHr-5KI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ONI CSS Tour (Part 2) Sogmian Neighborhoods<\/a> &#8211; With Map<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"fleet-viewer\">Fleet Viewer &#8211; retired<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The Fleet Viewer is where you can explore your fleet of Star Atlas ships in a space hanger.  The hanger is built with the same technology that is powering SAGE.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-guide\/how-to-see-star-atlas-ship-in-fleet-viewer\/\">How to see your Star Atlas ships in the Fleet Viewer<\/a>?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"sagelabs\">SAGE Labs &#8211; retired<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">SAGE Labs<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/sage-labs-a-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SAGE LABS \u2013 A GUIDE<\/a> by Aephia<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/sage-labs-the-missing-manual-part-1\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SAGE LABS \u2013 THE MISSING MANUAL \u2013 PART 1<\/a> by Aephia<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">SAGE Labs Guide by Beyond the Horizon<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/BTH2620\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Beyond the Horizon 2620<\/a> has created a video guide about how to play SAGE Labs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 1: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=k9HqW0iLRQM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Intro To Sage Labs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 2: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/QuDzYmFkTTc?si=BCt89RUsXT41_kDr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Create A Solana Native Wallet<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 3: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/PpMFvLMr7yo?si=YRiaMcS0Ch50ABfV\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Choosing A Faction<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 4: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/Xl2uuuSkrXM?si=eCCpa5cO7wddkfZT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Navigating The Marketplace<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 5: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/grqvEQ_vHBw?si=qt3VUqGxe1URfdZu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ship classes and Specs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 6: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/siGkI0wCDoM?si=onvkfRr9-p5GmYCZ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How To Buy A Ship<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 7: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/DPm0vHJKm14?si=rGIac9YkImLzNbkc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Navigate Sage Labs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 8: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/F8CHHnnM_y4?si=9A6APS0Y8cde9AO7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How To Import A Ship Into Sage Labs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 9: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/pzCyKBZO6to?si=5baKS5oJT6KS0TMg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How To Mine In Sage Labs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 10: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=Atgd0wksp4s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How To Craft In Sage Labs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 11: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/OWx_5lvT9Og?si=m7KjEyMAUjRFq7eT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How To Scan For SDUs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 12: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/6eUwOaUZSVs?si=JYe_mePXzZVfyYxg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Lets Build Some Fleets For Sage Labs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 13: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/KHOHXY9vOBQ?si=SpulyaoMeyLlBrFn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Set Up A Supply Chain In Sage Labs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 14: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/gMsKyT530C0?si=jZQg2RNxfJdyBSWc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Play Sage Labs On Mobile Devices<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>How To Play Star Atlas Part 15: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/WFb7NaK869g?si=EZsJ1VWIoNbCFqTX\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How to Access The Showroom<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Intergalactic Herald has created a guide on how to play Star Atlas. This &#8220;how to play Star Atlas guide&#8221; is a step-by-step outline of everything you need to get started with Star Atlas. The guide has three main parts: The guide also includes links to other Star Atlas content creators, resources and tools. Check out [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3}